# Code
```
class Solution {
    public long minimalKSum(int[] nums, int k) {
        TreeSet<Integer> set=new TreeSet<>();

        for(int number:nums)
            set.add(number);

        long sum=((long)k * (long)(k+1))/ 2;
        int count=0;

        for(Integer i:set){
            if(i>k)
                break;
            else{
                sum-=i;
                count++;
            }
        }
        int i=k+1;

        while(count>0){
            if(!set.contains(i)){
                sum+=i;
                count--;
            }
            i++;
        }
        return sum;
    }
}
```

