# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

By seeing the constraints it is obvious we can not iterate over k. As k is $10^8$ So iterating over k and nums will be too much time.
This gives the intuition of using math that sum of first n number is $n*(n+1)/2$
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
First we are sorting the nums so as to get the minimum numbers in the beginning.
We start temp as 1. And check for every $nums[i]$.
If $temp==nums[i]$ we update temp as $nums[i]+1$.
Now we check if number of elements between nums[i] and temp is less than k or not. 
If number of elements between temp and nums[i] is less than k. We add those elements in the answer and update temp as nums[i]+1. and update k as  k - (number of elements added).
If number of elements is greater than k. we add the elements from temp to temp+k-1 and update k as 0.

There is a case when we might end with nums array and still k is not 0. So we have to take care of this case also.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: $O(nlogn)$
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: $O(1)$
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    long long summ(long long  start, long long end)
    {
        if(start>end) return 0;
        return (end*(end+1)/2 - (start-1)*(start)/2);
    }
    long long minimalKSum(vector<int>& nums, int k) 
    {
        std::ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
        cin.tie(NULL);
        cout.tie(NULL);
       sort(nums.begin(),nums.end());
       long long temp=1;
       long long ans=0;
       for(int i  =0;i<nums.size();i++)
       {
           if(nums[i]==temp) temp = nums[i]+1;
           else if(nums[i]-temp <k)
           {
               ans = ans + summ(temp,nums[i]-1);
               if(nums[i]>temp)k = k - (nums[i]-temp);
               temp = nums[i]+1;
           }
           else if(nums[i]-temp >=k)
           {
               ans = ans+summ(temp,temp+k-1);
               k=0;
               break;
           }
       }
       if(k!=0)
       {
           ans = ans+summ(temp,temp+k-1);
           k=0;
       }
       return ans;


    }
};
```

